Package: yart
Type: Package
Title: RMarkdown Template for writing PDF reports
Version: 0.1.3
Author: Sebastian Sauer
Maintainer: Sebastian Sauer <ssauer@posteo.de>
Description: This package provides a simple wrapper around the pandoc
    template for LaTeX based pdf documents. A number of variables are 
    provided for convenience such as title, author, course name, 
    supervisor name, adress, and more.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
URL: https://github.com/sebastiansauer/yart
BugReports: https://github.com/sebastiansauer/yart/issues
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends:
    R (>= 2.11.1)
Imports:
  rmarkdown (>= 1.3),
  knitr (>= 1.10.5),
  yaml
Suggests:
    xtable,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
